snippet.textDisplay: 4 years back.... When I was going through my worst breakup and I used to be crying all day night, not talking much to anyone... One fine day I overheard my dad saying "kya hua h ise.. Aaj kal aisi shant shant kyu rehti h"... And at that moment I thought how we hurt ourselves over someone who don't even care.... Without thinking of those who actually cares... They get hurt whenever they see us sad cz they actually sacrifice alot for us, do alot for us... So then I started pretending to be happy... And now's the time... When I'm actually able to handle myself very well... And love my parents whom we generally tend to take granted... ❣️They're much more precious than we can ever realize❣️
